column4: everything is supposed to be great with ubuntu, but nothing works out of the box. Ok.. could someone assist me on a eFaz-GTK? I got a error:GPL Ghostscript 8.71: Unrecoverable error, exit code 1
... Googleing it brings me to almost useless fixes. Appearently years ago efax was STILL barely supported, so people have a bunch of errors, and issues. but barely any fixes..
Please don't flood, use http://paste.ubuntu.com to paste, don't use Enter as punctuation.
